262. , (12 pages); Refaat, A.A., Attia, N.K., Sibak, H.A., El Sheltawy, S.T., El Diwani, G.I., Production optimization and quality assessment of biodiesel from waste vegetable oil (2008) Int. J. Environ. Sci. Tech, 5 (1), pp. 75-82. , (8 pages); Shafipour, M.M., Farsiabi, M.M., An environmental economic analysis for reducing energy subsidies (2007) Int. J. Environ. Res, 1 (2), pp. 150-162. , (13 pages); Tehrani, S.M., Karbassi, A.R., Application of E-Commerce in local home-shopping and its consequences on energy consumption and air pollution reduction. Iran (2005) J. Environ. Health Sci. Eng, 2 (4), pp. 247-250. , (4 pages); Tehrani, S.M., Karbassi, A.R., Ghoddosi, J., Monavvari, S.M., Mirbagheri, S.A., Prediction of energy consumption and urban air pollution reduction in e-shopping adoption (2009) J. Food, Agric. Environ, 7 (3-4), pp. 132-137. , (6 pages); Timilsina, G.R., Shrestha, R.M., A general equilibrium analysis of potential demand side management programs in the household sector in Thailand (2008) I. J. Energ. Sec. Manage, 2 (4), pp. 570-593. , (23 pages); Utlu, Z., Sogut, Z., Hepbasli, A., Oktay, Z., Energy and exergy analyses of a raw mill in a cement production (2006) Appl. Therm. Eng, 26 (17-18), pp. 2479-2489. , (11 pages); Zare, D., Chen, G., Evaluation of a simulation model in predicting the drying parameters for deep-bed paddy drying (2009) Comput. Electron. Agri, 68 (1), pp. 78-87. , (10 pages); Zerrouqi, Z., Sbaa, M., Oujidi, M., Elkharmouz, M., Bengamra, S., Zerrouqi, A., Assessment of cement's dust impact on the soil using principal component analysis and GIS (2008) Int. J. Environ. Sci. Tech, 5 (1), pp. 125-134. , (10 pages)","Karbassi, A. R.; Graduate Faculty of the Environment, University of Tehran, P. O. Box 14155-6135, Tehran, Iran; email: akarbassi@ut.ac.ir",,,,,,,,17351472,,,,"English","Int. J. Environ. Sci. Technol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-73249152052
